{
  "info": {
    "name": "FaceMatchOnboardingFlow",
    "_postman_id": "facematch-onboarding-flow",
    "description": "Selfie<->document face match during driver onboarding (server-side IDfy face-compare for non-SDK uploads). FLAT structure (the dashboard parser is flat-only).\n\nSEED ONCE: UPDATE atlas_driver_offer_bpp.document_verification_config SET face_match_source_doc='ProfilePhoto' WHERE document_type IN ('DriverLicense','PanCard','AadhaarCard') AND merchant_operating_city_id IN (<city ids>);\n\nEDGE CASES (request name prefix = flow):\n  A selfie+PAN compare PASS -> PAN not INVALID    B selfie+PAN compare FAIL -> PAN INVALID\n  C PAN no-selfie -> not blocked (FMDeferred)      D is_a_match=null -> FAIL\n  E Aadhaar mismatch -> 400 FACE_MATCH_FAILED       F fail then re-upload+match -> clears INVALID\nNeeds the stack: `, run-mobility-stack-dev` + `, run-test-context-server`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "function r(){ return '9'+Math.floor(100000000+Math.random()*899999999); }",
          "if(!pm.collectionVariables.get('_test_png')) pm.collectionVariables.set('_test_png','iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==');",
          "['match','mismatch','C','D','E','F'].forEach(function(k){ var key='_test_driver_'+k; if(!pm.collectionVariables.get(key)) pm.collectionVariables.set(key, r()); });"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "_test_png",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "_test_driver_match",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "_test_driver_mismatch",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "_test_driver_C",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "_test_driver_D",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "_test_driver_E",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "_test_driver_F",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
